@startuml
title Notifications Module

class NotificationController {
  +list(recipientId, filters)
  +markRead(id)
  +markAllRead(recipientId)
  +send(payload)
  +broadcast(payload)
  +settings(recipientId)
  +updateSettings(recipientId, payload)
  +adminStats()
  +adminSystemAlert(payload)
}

class Notification {
  +id: string
  +recipientId: string
  +type: enum(session_reminder, pairing, feedback, progress, system)
  +title: string
  +content: string
  +channels: string[]
  +priority: enum(low, normal, high)
  +status: enum(unread, read)
  +createdAt: datetime
  +scheduledAt: datetime
}

class NotificationSetting {
  +recipientId: string
  +inApp: boolean
  +email: boolean
  +sms: boolean
}

class User {
  +id: string
  +role: string
}

NotificationController --> Notification
NotificationController --> NotificationSetting
User "1" -- "0..*" Notification : receives
User "1" -- "1" NotificationSetting

@enduml
